This script performs an automatic update of the dat files for Mcaffee Virus Scan command line for Linux

Requires:
 - uvscan
 - a bunch of perl modules

How to Install:

 1. Git way: download using git, so you can modify and contribute
 	Instructions pending

 2. Easy way: 
	# cd /usr/local/sbin
	# wget http://github.com/frankiejol/update_scan_dat/raw/master/update_scan_dat
	# chmod +x update_scan_dat

